Room.Name: Orchard Lane
Room.ShortDescription: You are walking along Orchard Lane, south of the Fiesty Kitten Nighclub.
Room.LongDescription: The Fiesty Kitten Nightclub and Bar is perhaps one of the most dangerous bars in all of Oceancrest. It is frequented by many officers of the city guard or other "peacekeeping" forces. The bar is also raided a lot by Morality Patrol for solicitation.
